      "title": "Health Impacts of Air Pollution",
      "content": {
        "text": "There are many health impacts associated with air pollution.  Opacity observations are one of the easiest and most effective ways to monitor and reduce air pollution.  By becoming a visible emissions observer, you are helping to reduce the deadliest form of pollution in the world.",
